{"tid":2229142,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Wifi6 router問題","createTime":"2020-10-04T07:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T06:18:10.000Z","uid":100251,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"df9e75de8858634b0bcf5f6c875204bfb6573191","tid":2229142,"uid":100251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:27:09.000Z","msg":"而家我用緊 netvigator 1000m寬頻 + $88/month  租Linksys EA9350 wifi6 router果個plan。<br />\n發覺成日有上唔到網嘅情況出現，<br />\n連住線冇斷到， 但就用唔到，要關一關 device個wifi再開返先可以重新用到。<br />\n約左師傅上黎睇，佢話如果屋企有唔係用wifi 6 嘅設備用緊同一個channel，就會有呢個怪情況出現。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家幫我set死左用 wifi5，但當我用 2.4ghz個頻譜上網時，依然有連住線但上唔到網嘅情況出現。<br />\n想請問其實係個router問題，定而家wifi6 嘅技術上嘅問題？<br />\n如果我換 ASUS ax86u or 88u , 情況會唔會改善到？"},{"pid":"ca3e691aabc287dcd9f80fefa6b7829b9f6abcae","tid":2229142,"uid":12259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:32:39.000Z","msg":"過熱 搵風扇吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2897233a94832a2903fb4e178adab68884ba3807","tid":2229142,"uid":100251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ca3e691aabc287dcd9f80fefa6b7829b9f6abcae","tid":2229142,"uid":12259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:32:39.000Z","msg":"過熱 搵風扇吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:36:01.000Z","msg":"應該唔係，摸都唔覺熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb219f9a0b08355effce08802c56ab80771a656","tid":2229142,"uid":130320,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:38:57.000Z","msg":"租router一年成千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e4ca22489ab84981054e4217b629ada301dfec","tid":2229142,"uid":72859,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bcb219f9a0b08355effce08802c56ab80771a656","tid":2229142,"uid":130320,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2