thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6pCvSno.jpg&h=227def84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰陣我係買左部新tablet ，佢一連wifi 就其他 devices 嘅 wifi 都有問題， 我reset 左手機同新嗰部tablet 就冇事了~<br />\n<br />\n另外set channel 嗰陣可以用 wifi analyzer <br />\n同埋可以係官網down firmware 手動更新~"},{"pid":"e015c8487ecccc1caabb8fb1aed7f61d67f55463","tid":2229142,"uid":377692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:45:30.000Z","msg":"set好哂之後 嗰ea9350 好穩好快 冇斷過~"},{"pid":"c7b0a756dbeeef9fae66d6a56e2023434599ad0e","tid":2229142,"uid":100251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e015c8487ecccc1caabb8fb1aed7f61d67f55463","tid":2229142,"uid":377692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:45:30.000Z","msg":"set好哂之後 嗰ea9350 好穩好快 冇斷過~"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T23:13:27.000Z","msg":"Set死咪冇左個wifi 6? <br />\n佢firmware得兩個option,  一係auto(自己係ac同 ax之間轉換),  一係就set死ac (wifi5)"},{"pid":"69abc19ad097981e61b6b9f4c5777de3d76eeda2","tid":2229142,"uid":377692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7b0a756dbeeef9fae66d6a56e2023434599ad0e","tid":2229142,"uid":100251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e015c8487ecccc1caabb8fb1aed7f61d67f55463","tid":2229142,"uid":377692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T15:45:30.000Z","msg":"set好哂之後 嗰ea9350 好穩好快 冇斷過~"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T23:13:27.000Z","msg":"Set死咪冇左個wifi 6? <br />\n佢firmware得兩個option,  一係auto(自己係ac同 ax之間轉換),  一係就set死ac (wifi5)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ejSWQ1Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FejSWQ1Y.png&h=2b6470ab&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我係咁set<br />\nset死通道唔會影響 wifi 6，你講嗰個應該係&quot;wifi 模式&quot; <br />\n如果通道set 做自動，佢會懶醒成日換通道 ，換通道嗰陣個wifi就會斷斷地。<br />\n同埋160mhz 大部分 devices 都唔支援，除左某部份支那機，set做80mhz 會穩定啲。"},{"pid":"7fda858fc128f75c29d5a72394233c4c86c607f2","tid":2229142,"uid":377692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020